Now implement Phase 2: manifest system, official file verification, file sync, and unknown file quarantine.

Do not redesign the UI from scratch.
Keep the premium minimal style already created.
Do not break existing settings, logs, or server status.

## Goal

The launcher should only allow official files listed in the manifest.
Users should not be able to add arbitrary mods, resource packs, shader packs, or config files inside the controlled instance.

## Fixed Paths

Instance folder:

```text
%LocalAppData%\ZzapchoRaidLauncher\instances\main
```

Quarantine folder:

```text
%LocalAppData%\ZzapchoRaidLauncher\quarantine
```

Protected directories:

- mods
- resourcepacks
- shaderpacks
- config

## Manifest Format

Create and support:

```json
{
  "schemaVersion": 1,
  "profileId": "zzapcho-raid-main",
  "displayName": "잡초 약탈서버",
  "manifestVersion": "2026.05.09-001",
  "server": {
    "host": "online.zzapcho.kr",
    "port": 25565
  },
  "minecraft": {
    "version": "1.21.4",
    "loader": "fabric",
    "loaderVersion": "0.16.9"
  },
  "launcher": {
    "minimumVersion": "1.0.0",
    "latestVersion": "1.0.0"
  },
  "sync": {
    "deleteUnknownFiles": false,
    "quarantineUnknownFiles": true,
    "protectedDirectories": [
      "mods",
      "resourcepacks",
      "shaderpacks",
      "config"
    ]
  },
  "files": [
    {
      "path": "mods/zzapcho-integrity-client.jar",
      "url": "https://github.com/OWNER/REPO/releases/download/client-2026.05.09/zzapcho-integrity-client.jar",
      "sha256": "PUT_SHA256_HERE",
      "size": 123456,
      "required": true
    },
    {
      "path": "resourcepacks/zzapcho-pack.zip",
      "url": "https://github.com/OWNER/REPO/releases/download/client-2026.05.09/zzapcho-pack.zip",
      "sha256": "PUT_SHA256_HERE",
      "size": 123456,
      "required": true
    }
  ],
  "signature": "PUT_SIGNATURE_HERE"
}
```

## Services To Implement

- ManifestDownloader
- ManifestParser
- ManifestValidator
- ManifestSignatureVerifier
- FileHashVerifier
- FileDownloader
- FileSyncService
- QuarantineService
- FileSetHashService

Use interfaces where it improves testability.

## Rules

1. Download or load manifest.
2. Validate schema version.
3. Validate required fields.
4. Verify manifest signature with an embedded public key.
5. Do not embed private keys.
6. Generate manifest hash.
7. Verify all files by SHA-256.
8. Download missing files.
9. Re-download files with incorrect hash.
10. Move unknown files in protected directories to quarantine.
11. Never scan outside the launcher instance folder.
12. Never scan the entire user PC.
13. Block Play button if required files are missing or invalid.
14. Show progress in the Update screen.

## Security Requirements

- Prevent path traversal such as ../../evil.exe.
- Only allow relative paths inside the instance folder.
- Use atomic downloads: download to temp file, verify hash, then move into place.
- Do not execute downloaded files.
- Log all actions without leaking secrets.

## UI Text

Use calm Korean text:

- 파일 확인 중
- 필요한 파일 다운로드 중
- 공식 클라이언트 구성과 다른 파일을 정리했습니다.
